            "id": "devotion",
            "type": "devotion",
            "title": "Daily Devotional",
            "value": "%3Cp%3EGiving%20is%20based%20on%20motives%2C%20and%20in%201%20Chronicles%2029%20David%20listed%20the%20right%20reasons%20for%20giving%20to%20God.%20First%2C%20he%20spoke%20about%20his%20own%20giving%20(vv.%202-3).%20Leaders%20have%20no%20business%20instructing%20others%20to%20give%20if%20they%20themselves%20have%20not%20given!%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3ESecond%2C%20David%20challenged%20the%20leaders%20under%20him%20to%20give%2C%20and%20they%20responded%20willingly.%20Joyfully%20they%20provided%20an%20abundance%20of%20gold%2C%20silver%2C%20bronze%2C%20iron%2C%20and%20precious%20stones%20for%20the%20construction%20of%20the%20temple%20(vv.%207-8).%20%20Because%20they%20had%20given%20freely%20and%20generously%20from%20their%20hearts%2C%20King%20David%20was%20filled%20with%20joy%20(v.%209).%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EThird%2C%20David%20motivated%20the%20congregation%20to%20give.%20David%20reminded%20them%20in%20his%20prayer%20before%20them%20that%20everything%20comes%20from%20God%20(v.%2014)%20and%20that%20they%20were%20only%20giving%20back%20to%20Him%20what%20He%20had%20given%20them%20in%20the%20first%20place.%20He%20then%20recalled%20the%20fact%20that%20they%20were%20only%20aliens%20passing%20through%20this%20world%2C%20using%20their%20earthly%20resources%20for%20a%20limited%20time%20called%20life%20(v.%2015).%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EFinally%2C%20David%20revealed%20that%20he%20had%20given%20with%20pure%20motives%20in%20the%20integrity%20of%20his%20heart%2C%20with%20no%20desire%20to%20impress%20or%20manipulate%20others%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3E(v.%2017).%20That%20made%20his%20giving%20acceptable%20to%20God.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EWhy%20should%20we%20greedily%20grasp%20for%20the%20passing%20things%20of%20this%20life%20when%20they%20will%20only%20slip%20through%20our%20fingers%20on%20the%20day%20we%20enter%20eternity%3F%20If%20our%20giving%20follows%20the%20guidelines%20David%20laid%20out%2C%20the%20Kingdom%20of%20God%20will%20be%20financed%20properly%2C%20sacrificially%2C%20and%20abundantly!%20%3C%2Fp%3E%0A"
        },
