            "api_nlt_to_ref": "Chronicles.28:1-29:30",
            "value": "%3Cdiv%20class%3D%22%20NLT%20NLT%20BibleText%20section%22%3E%3Csection%3E%3Ch2%20class%3D%22bk_ch_vs_header%22%3E1%20Chronicles%2028%3A1-29%3A30%2C%20NLT%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22chr1_28_1%22%20bk%3D%22chr1%22%20ch%3D%2228%22%20vn%3D%221%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22chapter-number%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw%22%3E1%20Chronicles%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23xA0%3B%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw_ch%22%3E28%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22subhead%22%3EDavid%26%23x2019%3Bs%20Instructions%20to%20Solomon%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-ch-hd%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E1%3C%2Fspan%3EDavid%20summoned%20all%20the%20officials%20of%20Israel%20to%20Jerusalem%26%23x2014%3Bthe%20leaders%20of%20the%20tribes%2C%20the%20commanders%20of%20the%20army%20divisions%2C%20the%20other%20generals%20and%20captains%2C%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E28%3A1%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Hebrew%20%3Cem%3Ethe%20commanders%20of%20thousands%20and%20commanders%20of%20hundreds.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%20the%20overseers%20of%20the%20royal%20property%20and%20livestock%2C%20the%20palace%20officials%2C%20the%20mighty%20men%2C%20and%20all%20the%20other%20brave%20warriors%20in%20the%20kingdom.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22chr1_28_2%22%20bk%3D%22chr1%22%20ch%3D%2228%22%20vn%3D%222%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E2%3C%2Fspan%3EDavid%20rose%20to%20his%20feet%20and%20said%3A%20%26%23x201C%3BMy%20brothers%20and%20my%20people!%20It%20was%20my%20desire%20to%20build%20a%20Temple%20where%20the%20Ark%20of%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x2019%3Bs%20Covenant%2C%20God%26%23x2019%3Bs%20footstool%2C%20could%20rest%20permanently.%20I%20made%20the%20necessary%20preparations%20for%20building%20it%2C%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22chr1_28_3%22%20bk%3D%22chr1%22%20ch%3D%2228%22%20vn%3D%223%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E3%3C%2Fspan%3Ebut%20God%20said%20to%20me%2C%20%26%23x2018%3BYou%20must%20not%20build%20a%20Temple%20to%20honor%20my%20name%2C%20for%20you%20are%20a%20warrior%20and%20have%20shed%20much%20blood.%26%23x2019%3B%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22chr1_28_4%22%20bk%3D%22chr1%22%20ch%3D%2228%22%20vn%3D%224%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E4%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BYet%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%2C%20the%20God%20of%20Israel%2C%20has%20chosen%20me%20from%20among%20all%20my%20father%26%23x2019%3Bs%20family%20to%20be%20king%20over%20Israel%20forever.%20For%20he%20has%20chosen%20the%20tribe%20of%20Judah%20to%20rule%2C%20and%20from%20among%20the%20families%20of%20Judah%20he%20chose%20my%20father%26%23x2019%3Bs%20family.%20And%20from%20among%20my%20father%26%23x2019%3Bs%20sons%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20was%20pleased%20to%20make%20me%20king%20over%20all%20Israel.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22chr1_28_5%22%20bk%3D%22chr1%22%20ch%3D%2228%22%20vn%3D%225%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E5%3C%2Fspan%3EAnd%20from%20among%20my%20sons%26%23x2014%3Bfor%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20has%20given%20me%20many%26%23x2014%3Bhe%20chose%20Solomon%20to%20succeed%20me%20on%20the%20throne%20of%20Israel%20and%20to%20rule%20over%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x2019%3Bs%20kingdom.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22chr1_28_6%22%20bk%3D%22chr1%22%20ch%3D%2228%22%20vn%3D%226%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E6%3C%2Fspan%3EHe%20said%20to%20me%2C%20%26%23x2018%3BYour%20son%20Solomon%20will%20build%20my%20Temple%20and%20its%20courtyards%2C%20for%20I%20have%20chosen%20him%20as%20my%20son%2C%20and%20I%20will%20be%20his%20father.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22chr1_28_7%22%20bk%3D%22chr1%22%20ch%3D%2228%22%20vn%3D%227%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E7%3C%2Fspan%3EAnd%20if%20he%20continues%20to%20obey%20my%20commands%20and%20regulations%20as%20he%20does%20now%2C%20I%20will%20make%20his%20kingdom%20last%20forever.%26%23x2019%3B%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22chr1_28_8%22%20bk%3D%22chr1%22%20ch%3D%2228%22%20vn%3D%228%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E8%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BSo%20now%2C%20with%20God%20as%20our%20witness%2C%20and%20in%20the%20sight%20of%20all%20Israel%26%23x2014%3Bthe%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x2019%3Bs%20assembly%26%23x2014%3BI%20give%20you%20this%20charge.%20Be%20careful%20to%20obey%20all%20the%20commands%20of%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20your%20God%2C%20so%20that%20you%20may%20continue%20to%20possess%20this%20good%20land%20and%20leave%20it%20to%20your%20children%20as%20a%20permanent%20inheritance.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22chr1_28_9%22%20bk%3D%22chr1%22%20ch%3D%2228%22%20vn%3D%229%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E9%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BAnd%20Solomon%2C%20my%20son%2C%20learn%20to%20know%20the%20God%20of%20your%20ancestors%20intimately.%20Worship%20and%20serve%20him%20with%20your%20whole%20heart%20and%20a%20willing%20mind.%20For%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20sees%20every%20heart%20and%20knows%20every%20plan%20and%20thought.%20If%20you%20seek%20him%2C%20you%20will%20find%20him.%20But%20if%20you%20forsake%20him%2C%20he%20will%20reject%20you%20forever.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22chr1_28_10%22%20bk%3D%22chr1%22%20ch%3D%2228%22%20vn%3D%2210%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E10%3C%2Fspan%3ESo%20take%20this%20seriously.%20The%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20has%20chosen%20you%20to%20build%20a%20Temple%20as%20his%20sanctuary.%20Be%20strong%2C%20and%20do%20the%20work.%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22chr1_28_11%22%20bk%3D%22chr1%22%20ch%3D%2228%22%20vn%3D%2211%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E11%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20David%20gave%20Solomon%20the%20plans%20for%20the%20Temple%20and%20its%20surroundings%2C%20including%20the%20entry%20room%2C%20the%20storerooms%2C%20the%20upstairs%20rooms%2C%20the%20inner%20rooms%2C%20and%20the%20inner%20sanctuary%26%23x2014%3Bwhich%20was%20the%20place%20of%20atonement.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22chr1_28_12%22%20bk%3D%22chr1%22%20ch%3D%2228%22%20vn%3D%2212%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E12%3C%2Fspan%3EDavid%20also%20gave%20Solomon%20all%20the%20plans%20he%20had%20in%20mind%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E28%3A12%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Or%20%3Cem%3Ethe%20plans%20of%20the%20spirit%20that%20was%20with%20him.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%20for%20the%20courtyards%20of%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x2019%3Bs%20Temple%2C%20the%20outside%20rooms%2C%20the%20treasuries%2C%20and%20the%20rooms%20for%20the%20gifts%20dedicated%20to%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22chr1_28_13%22%20bk%3D%22chr1%22%20ch%3D%2228%22%20vn%3D%2213%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E13%3C%2Fspan%3EThe%20king%20also%20gave%20Solomon%20the%20instructions%20concerning%20the%20work%20of%20the%20various%20divisions%20of%20priests%20and%20Levites%20in%20the%20Temple%20of%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E.%20And%20he%20gave%20specifications%20for%20the%20items%20in%20the%20Temple%20that%20were%20to%20be%20used%20for%20worship.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22chr1_28_14%22%20bk%3D%22chr1%22%20ch%3D%2228%22%20vn%3D%2214%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E14%3C%2Fspan%3EDavid%20gave%20instructions%20regarding%20how%20much%20gold%20and%20silver%20should%20be%20used%20to%20make%20the%20items%20needed%20for%20service.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22chr1_28_15%22%20bk%3D%22chr1%22%20ch%3D%2228%22%20vn%3D%2215%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E15%3C%2Fspan%3EHe%20told%20Solomon%20the%20amount%20of%20gold%20needed%20for%20the%20gold%20lampstands%20and%20lamps%2C%20and%20the%20amount%20of%20silver%20for%20the%20silver%20lampstands%20and%20lamps%2C%20depending%20on%20how%20each%20would%20be%20used.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22chr1_28_16%22%20bk%3D%22chr1%22%20ch%3D%2228%22%20vn%3D%2216%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E16%3C%2Fspan%3EHe%20designated%20the%20amount%20of%20gold%20for%20the%20table%20on%20which%20the%20Bread%20of%20the%20Presence%20would%20be%20placed%20and%20the%20amount%20of%20silver%20for%20other%20tables.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22chr1_28_17%22%20bk%3D%22chr1%22%20ch%3D%2228%22%20vn%3D%2217%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E17%3C%2Fspan%3EDavid%20also%20designated%20the%20amount%20of%20gold%20for%20the%20solid%20gold%20meat%20hooks%20used%20to%20handle%20the%20sacrificial%20meat%20and%20for%20the%20basins%2C%20pitchers%2C%20and%20dishes%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20amount%20of%20silver%20for%20every%20dish.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22chr1_28_18%22%20bk%3D%22chr1%22%20ch%3D%2228%22%20vn%3D%2218%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E18%3C%2Fspan%3EHe%20designated%20the%20amount%20of%20refined%20gold%20for%20the%20altar%20of%20incense.%20Finally%2C%20he%20gave%20him%20a%20plan%20for%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x2019%3Bs%20%26%23x201C%3Bchariot%26%23x201D%3B%26%23x2014%3Bthe%20gold%20cherubim%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E28%3A18%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Hebrew%20%3Cem%3Efor%20the%20gold%20cherub%20chariot.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%20whose%20wings%20were%20stretched%20out%20over%20the%20Ark%20of%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x2019%3Bs%20Covenant.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22chr1_28_19%22%20bk%3D%22chr1%22%20ch%3D%2228%22%20vn%3D%2219%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E19%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BEvery%20part%20of%20this%20plan%2C%26%23x201D%3B%20David%20told%20Solomon%2C%20%26%23x201C%3Bwas%20given%20to%20me%20in%20writing%20from%20the%20hand%20of%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E.%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E28%3A19%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Or%20%3Cem%3Ewas%20written%20under%20the%20direction%20of%20the%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ci%20class%3D%22tn-sc-ital%22%3ELord%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22chr1_28_20%22%20bk%3D%22chr1%22%20ch%3D%2228%22%20vn%3D%2220%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E20%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20David%20continued%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BBe%20strong%20and%20courageous%2C%20and%20do%20the%20work.%20Don%26%23x2019%3Bt%20be%20afraid%20or%20discouraged%2C%20for%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20God%2C%20my%20God%2C%20is%20with%20you.%20He%20will%20not%20fail%20you%20or%20forsake%20you.%20He%20will%20see%20to%20it%20that%20all%20the%20work%20related%20to%20the%20Temple%20of%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20is%20finished%20correctly.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22chr1_28_21%22%20bk%3D%22chr1%22%20ch%3D%2228%22%20vn%3D%2221%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E21%3C%2Fspan%3EThe%20various%20divisions%20of%20priests%20and%20Levites%20will%20serve%20in%20the%20Temple%20of%20God.%20Others%20with%20skills%20of%20every%20kind%20will%20volunteer%2C%20and%20the%20officials%20and%20the%20entire%20nation%20are%20at%20your%20command.%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22chr1_29_1%22%20bk%3D%22chr1%22%20ch%3D%2229%22%20vn%3D%221%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%